{"tid":2221562,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民陣十一遊行上訴遭駁回 維持發出反對通知書","createTime":"2020-09-28T12:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T13:03:02.000Z","uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5e758c36fb10f939280ddee4f0686a353296f64b","tid":2221562,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:48:44.000Z","msg":"【即時】(20:47) 民陣申請十一遊行遭警方發出反對通知書，公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會傍晚進行上訴聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n在長達兩個半小時的聆訊後，委員會一致決定駁回上訴，稱遊行會對公眾安全造成嚴重威脅，加上在疫情下，決定維持發出反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/inmediahknet/10970\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet%2F10970&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hISrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=edf7f5c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/inmediahknet/10970</a>"},{"pid":"8aae8e52190b441668dcb10560a546939b847e26","tid":2221562,"uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"十一 街頭見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E41fYZn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE41fYZn.jpg&h=0795580e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5qcF953.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5qcF953.jpg&h=879a2ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qm2SgL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqm2SgL4.jpg&h=7855fde8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efeba8f9eb4492ad00066cb4326b8d7042031a3f","tid":2221562,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"有冇得再申請"},{"pid":"7843a51bd8b9322c480a3757ddea43fcb5d34f1a","tid":2221562,"uid":70489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:50:39.000Z","msg":"十一港島見"},{"pid":"5418b53e87df9fdf350a68bcc5d3c7358813fbf2","tid":2221562,"uid":4151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:50:47.000Z","msg":"聽講中央話要高調慶祝國慶"},{"pid":"48326124eca7160a41f88ee973669bbe08ed8912","tid":2221562